### Auth Requests

# @name register
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "superadmin@maildrop.cc",
    "password": "Password123!",
    "name": "MD Super Admin"
}

###

# @name verify
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "superadmin@maildrop.cc",
    "otp": "496418" 
}
# Note: Get the real OTP from the server console/logs. This only verifies the account.

###

# @name resendOtp
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/resend-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "md@maildrop.cc"
}

###

# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "md2@maildrop.cc",
    "password": "Password123!"
}

